The '''Pembric Security Legionnaires''' were [[Pembric II]]'s [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceport]] and possible planetary security force under the [[Pembric Security Legion]]. Each Legionnaire wore a white uniform, blast helmet and vest. Primarily [[Human/Legends|Human]], they patrolled in groups of five or six, and were heavily armed. In [[8 ABY/Legends|8 ABY]], Chief Magistrate [[Kebbo]] led the Legionnaires. They enforced the will of the [[Bombaasa Cartel]] on [[Pembric II]], and were used to quell civilian protesters at [[Erwithat Spaceport]]. By [[19 ABY/Legends|19 ABY]], they were led by [[Lieutenant/Legends|Lieutenant]] [[Maxiti]].

